name: WarpSpeed
overview: In Your Face Combat Against A Swarming Alien Armada! WarpSpeed's incredible 3-D graphics and cockpit perspective put you so close to the combat that your eyebrows may get fried. You're the bad dude of deep space, piloting a hyper-fast, heavily armed Starfighter against the evil Alien Horde. Your mission? Blow the crater faced mutants back to their black holes before they can burn Earth to a crisp.
